{"tid":930153,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人部iPhone Xs／Xs Max Wifi 有問題?","createTime":"2018-12-06T05:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T17:08:19.000Z","uid":167573,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e98b947c9a2f349c40f48d5758b6e7f6fb005772","tid":930153,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"我部 iPhone xs 成日耐唔耐都會有咁嘅情況發生.<br />\n部電話連住wifi嘅, 但上上下網或者用緊instagram嘅時候突然load死咗. 無咗internet.<br />\n有時睇睇下片就會停咗. 通常要等1-2分鐘後refresh safari 個page, load到出嚟就正常返.<br />\n我係佢停咗上網個陣用部舊iPhone上網, 用ig...係完全正常.<br />\n同埋已經試咗restart 同update router firmware.所以我覺得應該唔關屋企router事. <br />\n跟住電話都試過reset networking setting. 又試過del app. <br />\n連DFC mode clean install 都試過都係有咁嘅問題出現.<br />\n但部電話係4G 情況下係完全無問題....<br />\n所以我都唔知係邊part出咗事.<br />\n啱啱先買咗部機一個月, 唔通咁快就要拎返apple 換service unit"},{"pid":"8ca701da4457fe067927d59a482df683178bbefe","tid":930153,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:22:20.000Z","msg":"推翻上去先"},{"pid":"c924e1c2a494813ec117faf538b110dd7565059f","tid":930153,"uid":96485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，但淨係喺屋企先會<br />\n平時熄咗電話wifi再開返就得<br />\n所以以為係屋企wifi問題"},{"pid":"c14dac164efa1a91f28acee1ed6b9ea82653ed89","tid":930153,"uid":50872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ddc182c7b1418a5be1c684cafbcfb0c3ac6d0e","tid":930153,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"用乜乜link就抵、死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec25d8a5bb9b26a6ba6a0dc3f3dd4fa41ac1f0cc","tid":930153,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score